OL,3,CUnwrapped: Christmas Costs and Cons
OL,5,FFestive cheer is in the air again; and
OL,6,FChristmas lights are illuminating all
OL,7,Fover the land.
OL,9,FBut as many of us prepare for the
OL,10,Fseason of goodwill, what are some of
OL,11,Fthe risks and pitfalls that consumers
OL,12,Fhave to be on their guard against this
OL,13,FChristmas?
OL,15,FMartha Keith set up her stationery
OL,16,Fcompany - Martha Brook - ten years
OL,17,Fago, and it has since grown into a
OL,18,Fsuccessful business, selling premium
OL,19,Fstationery products from her office in
OL,20,FWest London.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
