OL,5,FOne of the company's most successful
OL,6,Fproducts is a stationery advent
OL,7,Fcalendar. And in the runup to
OL,8,FChristmas, it's a best seller.
OL,10,FAfter launching this year's calendar
OL,11,Fin September, it sold out within a
OL,12,Fweek. But then, Martha started to
OL,13,Fnotice something unusual.
OL,15,FScammers had stolen some of her
OL,16,FInstagram reels and TikTok videos and
OL,17,Fwere running them as ads across
OL,18,Fvarious social networking sites,
OL,19,Fsending people to fraudulent websites
OL,20,Fwith her photos on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
