OL,5,FTo find out how savvy people really
OL,6,Fare about keeping themselves safe from
OL,7,Fonline fraudsters, we came to Nuneaton
OL,8,Fmarket, with a proposition for the
OL,9,Fpublic that was too good to be true.
OL,10,FWe offered members of the public a
OL,11,Ffree christmas present, for filling in
OL,12,Fwhat they thought was an innocent
OL,13,Fsurvey about people's habits on
OL,14,FChristmas day.
OL,16,FBut what we were really interested in
OL,17,Fwas the 'about you' section of the
OL,18,Fform. This asked for personal data
OL,19,Fthat might be of use to scammers
OL,20,Fincluding full name, date of birth,
OL,21,Fmother's maiden name and a password.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
