OL,5,FOur tech experts ZOE EDMEADES from The
OL,6,FSecurity Company International (TSC)
OL,7,Fand SIMON NICHOLLS Keepnet Labs were
OL,8,Fwaiting in a nearby surveillance van,
OL,9,Freceiving live updates of what was
OL,10,Fbeing entered into the digital form.
OL,12,FAny data participants entered was
OL,13,Fencrypted, and our tech experts could
OL,14,Fonly see which sections had been
OL,15,Ffilled in, and not the data itself.
OL,17,FOur findings were shocking.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
