OL,3,CUnwrapped: Christmas Costs and Cons
OL,5,FOf the people we tested, not one of
OL,6,Fthem hesitated to give away their
OL,7,Fpersonal data in exchange for a glitzy
OL,8,Fbox of chocs.
OL,10,FBut beyond the ever present risk of
OL,11,Fscammers, there are more risks to
OL,12,Fconsumers this Christmas. For many of
OL,13,Fus, electronic goods will have pride
OL,14,Fof place on our Christmas lists, but
OL,15,Fparticularly for high powered
OL,16,Felectronics, the risks can be
OL,17,Fsignificant. Ebikes and e-scooters are
OL,18,Fincreasingly popular, but there has
OL,19,Fbeen a rise in the number of fires
OL,20,Fassociated with them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
