OL,5,FThe London fire brigade recently said
OL,6,Fthere had been 155 e-bike fires in
OL,7,F2023, up by 78% from the previous year.
OL,9,FWe spoke to Giuseppe Capanna from
OL,10,FElectrical Safety First who told us
OL,11,Fhow quickly things can go wrong when
OL,12,Fusing an incorrect charger for an
OL,13,Febike battery.
OL,15,FHis advice was clear; "if you've
OL,16,Falready got an e-bike or e-scooter and
OL,17,Fyou lose the charger, make sure you go
OL,18,Fback to the source to buy a
OL,19,Freplacement charger".
