OL,5,FHe emphasised though that ebike
OL,6,Ftechnology - when used correctly and
OL,7,Fwhen chargers are bought from a
OL,8,Freputable supplier - is not inherently
OL,9,Funsafe.
OL,11,FBut even gifts that seem entirely
OL,12,Fharmless can present hidden risks. A
OL,13,Ffew years ago, Jacqueline's husband
OL,14,Fbought her a hot water bottle for
OL,15,FChristmas. It seemed like the perfect
OL,16,Fgift, but he never imagined it could
OL,17,Fbe the cause of a life changing injury.
OL,19,FAfter owning the hot water bottle for
OL,20,Fthree years, it split and severely
OL,21,Fburned her leg.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
