OL,5,F"I'd have to use crutches cos I
OL,6,Fcouldn't put weight on it because it
OL,7,Fwould swell.. I just couldn't stand
OL,8,Fthe pain."
OL,10,FShe didn't know that hot water bottles
OL,11,Fare said to expire after a period of
OL,12,Ftime, and are considered no longer
OL,13,Fsafe.
OL,15,FAlthough there's no set limit, Trading
OL,16,FStandards say that hot water bottles
OL,17,Fshould be replaced two to three years
OL,18,Fafter their first use.
