OL,5,FShe was unaware that the date that a
OL,6,Fhot water bottle is manufactured can
OL,7,Fbe found on a so called 'daisy wheel'
OL,8,Fthat appears on most hot water
OL,9,Fbottles. The 'petals' of the daisy
OL,10,Frepresent months of the year, whilst
OL,11,Fthe number in the centre of the daisy
OL,12,Freveals the year of manufacture.
OL,14,FWe asked the people of Nuneaton if
OL,15,Fthey recognised it, and most people we
OL,16,Fspoke to couldn't tell us what it
OL,17,Fmeant.
